content.title: On Earth
content.content:
1918 - J.R.R. Tolkien attends a medical board examination while based at the Humber Garrison.
1952 - Actor Geoff Morrell is born.
1990 - Actor Luke Pasqualino is born.
2006 - Actor Wi Kuki Kaa dies.

content.title: In Arda
content.content:
T.A. 3019:
The Fellowship of the Ring travels south down the Anduin. Samwise spots Gollum on his log.
